  <section class="hero"><div class="wrap">
          <div class="crumb"><a href="/">Home</a> › <a href="/brands/">Brands</a> › <a href="/brands/miele/">Miele</a> › Refrigerator Repair</div>
          <h1>Miele Refrigerator Repair</h1>
          <p class="lede">
            Miele is the family-owned German refrigeration specialist — 125 years of Gütersloh-built precision, and
            one of three brands we service that architects spec on modernist LA integrated kitchens. MasterCool
            column refrigerators (K2000, K2700), PerfectCool freestanding, PerfectFresh humidity-controlled drawers,
